    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2260530/extras/7db8f1fe29f751e965696420b4fbff13.poster.avif?t=1771944952\" width=616 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2260530/extras/7db8f1fe29f751e965696420b4fbff13.webm?t=1771944952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>喵喵喵亲爱的朋友们！《纽约躲猫猫》，把猫猫全都找出来吧。<br>内容丰富、清新可爱的手绘风带来短小精致的治愈体验！从美丽的单色场景开始，放松身心，一只接一只地找出所有猫猫，揭开最终的全彩画作。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2260530/extras/0a6ad20028acdc4f763adf3613a77993.webp?t=1771944952\" width=21 height=20 /></span><strong>整个游戏共有 770 个可供寻找的隐藏目标！</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2260530/extras/0a6ad20028acdc4f763adf3613a77993.webp?t=1771944952\" width=21 height=20 /></span><strong>游玩不同的游戏模式，找到特殊猫猫，解锁附加关卡！</strong><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2260530/extras/74acf2f35d35838b0454f7532a6827b7.avif?t=1771944952\" width=616 height=172 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >普通模式</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>找到固定位置的 120 只猫猫。<br></li><li>3 次提示机会。</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >进阶模式</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>找到 200 只随机位置的猫猫。<br></li><li>12 只特殊猫猫，可解锁附加关卡。<br></li><li>找到 20 个城市居民，获得提示。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2260530/extras/1b60876b4778d466f86ac2fac9804b31.poster.avif?t=1771944952\" width=616 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2260530/extras/1b60876b4778d466f86ac2fac9804b31.webm?t=1771944952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>附加关卡的规模不同，猫咪数量也不尽相同。每个关卡有一次提示机会。<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>臭臭猫咖：</strong>50 只猫咪<br></li><li><strong>屋顶：</strong>50 只猫咪<br></li><li><strong>忍者猫总部：</strong>50 只猫咪<br></li><li><strong>地铁：</strong>75 只猫咪<br></li><li><strong>博物馆：</strong>100 只猫咪<br></li><li><strong>城镇公园：</strong>100 只猫咪</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2260530/extras/fb13ce1a199ccea2ee09e9b124d17e06.webp?t=1771944952\" width=600 height=18 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >辅助功能</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>暗色模式<br></li><li>反转鼠标缩放<br></li><li>鼠标拖曳灵敏度<br></li><li>屏幕边缘滚动</li></ul>",
